title: Robin Hobb - The Farseer Trilogy
description:
The Farseer Trilogy follows the life of FitzChivalry Farseer (Fitz), a trained assassin, in a kingdom called The Six Duchies while his uncle, Prince Verity, attempts to wage war on the Red-Ship Raiders fromThe OutIslands who are attacking the shores of the kingdom by turning the people of the Six Duchies into Forged ones; a form of zombification which makes them emotionless. Meanwhile Prince Regal's jealousy and the indulgence of his own selfish whims threatens to destroy Six Duchies.

Assassin's Apprentice [ISBN-10: 055357339X][ISBN-13: 9780553573398]
Royal Assassin [ISBN-10: 0553573411][ISBN-13: 9780553573411]

Author: Robin Hobb
